BT /F2 18 Tf 54.00 692.00 Td (1. Ultra-Short Summary) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 666.50 Td (Adult humans, just like children, have a built-in attachment system - a set of emotional and behavioral) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 651.65 Td (programs that regulate closeness with a romantic partner. This system is not pathology, not weakness,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 636.80 Td (not bad psychology. It is biology, the same way hunger and fear are biology.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 614.95 Td (People differ in how their attachment system reacts to closeness, distance, and conflict. Decades of) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 600.10 Td (research compress this variation into three working patterns:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 578.25 Td (Ģ Secure - comfortable with closeness and with autonomy. Reads partner signals accurately.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 563.95 Td (Recovers from conflict.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 545.65 Td (Ģ Anxious - hyper-tuned to signs of distance. Closeness calms; perceived distance triggers protest) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 531.35 Td (behavior.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 513.05 Td (Ģ Avoidant - hyper-tuned to signs of engulfment. Distance calms; closeness triggers deactivating) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 498.75 Td (strategies.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 480.45 Td (A fourth pattern \(disorganized / fearful-avoidant\) blends anxious and avoidant features and usually) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 465.60 Td (reflects more complex early experience or trauma.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 443.75 Td (The single most consequential idea in this whole field: many problems people interpret as 'we are) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 428.90 Td (incompatible' or 'something is wrong with me' are actually predictable interactions between two) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 414.05 Td (attachment systems. Once you can name the pattern, the situation stops being personal drama and) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 399.20 Td (becomes legible.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 377.35 Td (The single most consequential practical move: when choosing a long-term partner, weight attachment) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 362.50 Td (style at least as heavily as chemistry, looks, status, or shared interests. A secure partner is a force) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 347.65 Td (multiplier for your life. An avoidant partner paired with anxious style is a slow, painful loop that reliably) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 332.80 Td (damages both people.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 310.95 Td (Everything else in this guide is the unpacking of those two sentences.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 303.50 30.00 Td (3) Tj ET
