BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 666.50 Td (If you read nothing else, read these. Each one is a lever that, used correctly, changes outcomes in your) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 651.65 Td (love life.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 629.80 Td (Ģ Idea 1. Attachment style is descriptive, not destiny. It predicts your default reactions, not your fate.) Tj ET
