BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 597.20 Td (independent in the world, not less. Needing someone is not weakness.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 578.90 Td (Ģ Idea 3. Anxious and avoidant styles are mirror images. Both are activated by the same threat \(loss) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 564.60 Td (of equilibrium in closeness\) but solve it in opposite ways.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 546.30 Td (Ģ Idea 4. Anxious + avoidant pairings are statistically common and emotionally addictive. The) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 532.00 Td (intensity feels like love; it is mostly the attachment system flailing.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 513.70 Td (Ģ Idea 5. Secure people are systematically undervalued in early dating because their nervous) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 499.40 Td (systems do not generate the spikes we mistake for chemistry.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 481.10 Td (Ģ Idea 6. Most 'communication problems' in couples are really protest behavior or deactivation in) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 466.80 Td (disguise. Fix the attachment-level signal and the words follow.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 448.50 Td (Ģ Idea 7. Effective communication is direct, specific, non-blaming, and focused on needs - not on the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 434.20 Td (partner's personality. This is a learnable skill.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 415.90 Td (Ģ Idea 8. You can shift toward more secure functioning. It is slow and uncomfortable, not a) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 401.60 Td (personality transplant. The fastest path is a relationship with a secure partner plus deliberate) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 387.30 Td (self-work.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 369.00 Td (Ģ Idea 9. Early in dating, patterns are visible within weeks if you know what to look for. Most people) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 354.70 Td (see the signals but rationalize them away.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 336.40 Td (Ģ Idea 10. The relationship is the unit of analysis, not the individual. 'Are they good for me' beats 'are) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 322.10 Td (they a good person'.) Tj ET
