BT /F2 18 Tf 54.00 692.00 Td (7. Dating: How to Read a Partner Early) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 666.50 Td (Most relationship pain is preventable at the selection stage. By weeks 4-8 of dating, an attachment) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 651.65 Td (pattern is usually visible to anyone willing to look. The catch is that the spike-seeking part of the brain is) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 636.80 Td (highly motivated to look away.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54.00 595.95 Td (7.1 Stop confusing activation with chemistry) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 573.45 Td (When meeting someone new, ask: do I feel pulled in by interest in this specific human, or by) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 558.60 Td (uncertainty - wondering if they like me, decoding mixed signals, waiting for replies that come at random) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 543.75 Td (intervals? The first is interest. The second is your attachment system being activated by ambiguity.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 528.90 Td (They feel almost the same in the body. They are not the same thing.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 507.05 Td (Practical filter: if a person produces calm interest rather than nervous spikes, give them more time) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 492.20 Td (before you decide they are 'not it'. The boring-secure first impression is the most underrated signal in) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 477.35 Td (dating.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54.00 436.50 Td (7.2 Behavioral signals to watch) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 414.00 Td (These are not labels to slap on someone after one date. They are patterns to track over weeks.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54.00 379.15 Td (Signs of secure functioning \(green\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 359.15 Td (Ģ Replies are timely and consistent, without being performative. The pattern is steady.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 340.85 Td (Ģ Plans are concrete and actually happen.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 322.55 Td (Ģ Direct in stating preferences and limits, without hostility.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 304.25 Td (Ģ Asks about you, listens, remembers details next time.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 285.95 Td (Ģ Comfortable with both closeness and time apart - neither clings nor disappears.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 267.65 Td (Ģ Talks about exes neutrally; takes some responsibility for past relationship outcomes.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 249.35 Td (Ģ Conflict, when it shows up, is handled by talking it through, not by silent treatment or escalation.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54.00 218.05 Td (Signs of anxious patterning \(yellow\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 198.05 Td (Ģ Intense early enthusiasm, future-talk in week one.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 179.75 Td (Ģ Strong reactions to small delays.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 161.45 Td (Ģ Frequent reassurance-seeking, often disguised as compliments-fishing.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 143.15 Td (Ģ History of dramatic relationships described as 'crazy' or 'toxic' - usually the partner's fault.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54.00 111.85 Td (Signs of avoidant patterning \(yellow\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 91.85 Td (Ģ Reluctance to label or define anything.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 301.00 30.00 Td (13) Tj ET
