BT /F2 18 Tf 54.00 692.00 Td (8. Effective Communication: A Practical Method) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 666.50 Td (The slogan 'communicate better' is useless on its own. What actually helps is a small set of moves you) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 651.65 Td (can perform under pressure. Here is the method, distilled.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54.00 610.80 Td (8.1 The four properties of a good attachment message) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 588.30 Td (Ģ Direct: name the actual issue, not a proxy.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 570.00 Td (Ģ Specific: about a behavior or situation, not a personality verdict.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 551.70 Td (Ģ Non-blaming: own your feeling, do not assign motive.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 533.40 Td (Ģ Need-focused: state what you want, not just what is wrong.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 515.10 Td (Bad: 'You never make time for me. You don't care.' \(Vague, blaming, attributes motive, no clear ask.\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 493.25 Td (Better: 'When we go three days without seeing each other, I start to feel disconnected. Can we put) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 478.40 Td (something on the calendar this week?' \(Specific, owns the feeling, clear request.\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54.00 437.55 Td (8.2 Why this is so hard for anxious / avoidant people) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 415.05 Td (Anxious: stating a need directly feels dangerous because it surfaces the possibility that the answer is) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 400.20 Td (no. Protest behavior is a way to test the bond without stating the need plainly. The cost is that the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 385.35 Td (partner experiences attack rather than request.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 363.50 Td (Avoidant: stating a need directly feels dangerous because it concedes that one is needed at all.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 348.65 Td (Deactivation is a way to keep the felt independence intact. The cost is that the partner experiences) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 333.80 Td (rejection where there was, in reality, ordinary closeness pressure.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 311.95 Td (The fix is the same on both sides: lower the perceived stakes of stating the need by stating it earlier,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 297.10 Td (smaller, and more often. Big requests delivered at low frequency hit hard. Small requests delivered) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 282.25 Td (continuously become a normal soundtrack.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54.00 241.40 Td (8.3 The 'first response' test) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 218.90 Td (When you state a clean need, what your partner does in the first 30 seconds is data. It is not the whole) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 204.05 Td (person, but it is a real signal.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 182.20 Td (Ģ Helpful first responses: 'Tell me more.' 'I hear you.' 'Thanks for saying it directly.' 'Let me think for a) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 167.90 Td (moment.') Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 149.60 Td (Ģ Unhelpful first responses: defensiveness, counter-attack, dismissal, mocking the request, going) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 135.30 Td (silent for days.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 117.00 Td (If, over months, the unhelpful responses outnumber the helpful ones at a 3-to-1 rate, the bottleneck is) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 102.15 Td (not your delivery. It is fit.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 301.00 30.00 Td (15) Tj ET
