BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 666.50 Td (Every framework smuggles in unstated assumptions. Naming them does not invalidate the work; it tells) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 651.65 Td (you where to be careful when applying it.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54.00 610.80 Td (10.1 Three styles is enough) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 588.30 Td (The popular three-bucket model is a simplification of research that treats attachment as two continuous) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 573.45 Td (dimensions \(anxiety and avoidance\), which produces a 2D space rather than three discrete boxes. The) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 558.60 Td (three buckets are catchy and clinically useful, but real people sit on a continuum and shift contextually.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 543.75 Td (Treat the labels as lenses, not as IDs.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54.00 502.90 Td (10.2 Style is mostly a stable individual trait) Tj ET
