BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 465.55 Td (relational: style emerges in interaction with a specific partner and a specific moment. The same person) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 450.70 Td (can present anxious with one partner and secure with another. This matters because it means you are) Tj ET
