BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 421.00 Td (relationship.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54.00 380.15 Td (10.3 Heterosexual, monogamous, Western default) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 357.65 Td (Most of the popular framing - and many of the examples - assume a particular relationship structure.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 342.80 Td (The underlying biology of attachment is broader than that, but applying the framework outside the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 327.95 Td (default \(non-monogamy, queer relationships, cross-cultural norms about closeness\) requires more care) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 313.10 Td (than the popular write-up admits.) Tj ET
