BT /F2 18 Tf 54.00 692.00 Td (11. Where the Authors Are Right - And Where the Logic) Tj ET
BT /F2 18 Tf 54.00 669.50 Td (Bends) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 644.00 Td (A fair audit. The framework deserves credit and scrutiny in the same breath.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54.00 603.15 Td (11.1 Where they are clearly right) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 580.65 Td (Ģ Naming attachment as a biological system, not a personality flaw, is the single most useful) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 566.35 Td (reframe in popular psychology of the last 30 years. It removes shame and replaces it with) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 552.05 Td (mechanism.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 533.75 Td (Ģ The advice to weight attachment compatibility over spark in long-term partner choice is, on the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 519.45 Td (evidence, correct.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 501.15 Td (Ģ The dependency paradox is real and well-supported: secure connection produces more, not less,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 486.85 Td (exploration and resilience.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 468.55 Td (Ģ The tools for effective communication are sound and match independent findings from) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 454.25 Td (couples-therapy research.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 435.95 Td (Ģ The diagnosis of the anxious-avoidant trap is accurate and probably saves a non-trivial number of) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 421.65 Td (people from wasted years.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54.00 384.35 Td (11.2 Where the logic gets thinner) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 361.85 Td (Ģ Style as primary explanation. The framework is powerful, and like all powerful frameworks it tends) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 347.55 Td (to explain everything in its own terms. Real relationships involve trauma, mental health, life stage,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 333.25 Td (money, fertility, family-of-origin politics, and plain old values mismatch. Attachment is one lens, not) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 318.95 Td (the lens.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 300.65 Td (Ģ Determinism on partner selection. The advice 'choose secure' is correct on average, weak as a) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 286.35 Td (rule for an individual. People meet who they meet, and categorical filtering excludes humans who) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 272.05 Td (would be good for them.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 253.75 Td (Ģ Optimism about change vs honesty about cost. Becoming earned-secure is real, but it is years of) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 239.45 Td (work, not a chapter. The popular framing sometimes implies that recognizing the pattern is most of) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 225.15 Td (the battle. It is not. Recognizing it is move one of fifty.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 206.85 Td (Ģ The clean dichotomy avoidant vs anxious. Many people are mixed - anxious with closeness,) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 192.55 Td (avoidant with conflict; secure in long relationships, anxious in early dating. The clean labels are) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 178.25 Td (easier to teach but rougher than reality.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 159.95 Td (Ģ Asymmetric sympathy. Read carefully, the popular framing is more compassionate to anxious) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 145.65 Td (readers than to avoidant ones. Avoidance is treated as something to work around in a partner;) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 131.35 Td (anxiety is treated as something to soothe. The mirror image is rarer, and it should not be.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 54.00 94.05 Td (11.3 What is missing entirely from most popular write-ups) Tj ET
