BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 666.50 Td (If you do nothing else from this guide, do these.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 644.65 Td (Ģ 1. In long-term partner choice, weight attachment compatibility above chemistry. Calm is not) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 630.35 Td (boring; it is the precondition for everything else.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 612.05 Td (Ģ 2. Learn to tell activation apart from interest. Spike is not signal.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 593.75 Td (Ģ 3. Make small, direct, specific, non-blaming requests early and often. Watch the first response.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 575.45 Td (Ģ 4. Stop waiting for an avoidant partner to spontaneously transform inside an anxious-avoidant) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 561.15 Td (loop. They will not. The loop is the obstacle.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 542.85 Td (Ģ 5. Optimize for repair speed, not for never fighting.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 524.55 Td (Ģ 6. If you want to shift your own style, change the lived environment - not just your reading list.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 510.25 Td (Secure relationships, body practices, and slow deliberate exposure to the discomfort beat any) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 495.95 Td (amount of self-analysis.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 477.65 Td (Ģ 7. Treat the framework as a flashlight, not a courtroom. It is a way to see; it is not a verdict on you) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 463.35 Td (or your partner.) Tj ET
