BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 262.00 Td (Ģ When I state a small, direct need to a partner, my internal experience right after is _____.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 243.70 Td (Ģ If I imagine a perfectly available, calm, responsive partner, my first reaction is \(excitement /) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 229.40 Td (boredom / suspicion / relief / other\) _____. What that reveals is _____.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 211.10 Td (Ģ The recurring fight in my last relationship was really about \(closeness, autonomy, respect, fear of) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 70.00 196.80 Td (loss, control, fairness\) _____.) Tj ET
