stream
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 721.00 Td (The most honest thing this framework can give you is not a label, a partner, or a happy ending. It is a) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 706.15 Td (vocabulary. With a vocabulary, you stop being inside the storm; you can name what is happening while) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 691.30 Td (it is happening. That alone, repeated for years, is what changes lives. Not the labels. The seeing.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 54.00 669.45 Td (Use the framework as a tool. Drop it when it stops being useful. The point was never the theory.) Tj ET
